":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:07:14.000Z","msg":"學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始重諗,點解D人咁on9嘅問題都諗得出,緊係會啦<br />\n睇完個po之後原來自己先係井底之蛙,我先係on9仔"},{"pid":"c0bb2c915539172d6c210da646aac0b923b5d700","tid":644172,"uid":45431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"我又想問下，用樓主個case, 如果個盒大到一個地步，例如有成五百米長闊高，架模型機就飛到頂，反作用氣流未到地面就變左唔同方向既擾流，咁個結論有無唔同?"},{"pid":"407f0a989cc7e0c8451ce0e8408e4c3a8de1e75f","tid":644172,"uid":67976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c38fa012c4bcd510d8ed78a0b792721f2bff2d9","tid":644172,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e56905629bfd00b1b661cce0e449e2ad7f8bbd1","tid":644172,"uid":61398,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T00:56:47.000Z","msg":"是但啦就當佢半生半死啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T01:30:30.000Z","msg":"薜丁格的無人機"}]}